Class NonStandardPackage

java.lang.Object
components.Package
components.NonStandardPackage
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class NonStandardPackage
extends Package
Represents a package with non standard size
A non standard package is a Package with a specific width, length and height

3.0, 14/6/2021
